Hi,
this is the NeoMagic floating foint removal patch
I posted previously for Linux 2.4.18-pre9-ac3.
This one applies against Linux 2.5.5-pre1 and
updates the driver to version 0.3.2.
-- 
Best regards,
  Denis Oliver Kropp
